'''BT.1120''' is a digital interface standard for [[HDTV]] studio signals published by the [[International Telecommunication Union]].<ref name="Rec. ITU-R BT.1120-8">{{cite book|title=Recommendation ITU-R BT.1120-8 Digital interfaces for HDTV studio signals|date=January 2012|publisher=[[International Telecommunication Union]]|url=https://www.itu.int/dms_pubrec/itu-r/rec/bt/R-REC-BT.1120-8-201201-I!!PDF-E.pdf|accessdate=5 October 2017}}</ref>   {{asof|October 2017}}, the current version of BT.1120 is BT.1120-8.<ref>{{cite web|title=BT.1120 : Digital interfaces for HDTV studio signals|url=https://www.itu.int/rec/R-REC-BT.1120-8-201201-I/en|website=ITU-R|publisher=[[International Telecommunication Union]]|accessdate=5 October 2017}}</ref>

